author: Allan Smith
title: Fauci: Coronavirus could kill over 100,000 Americans
description: Dr. Anthony Fauci said Sunday that hundreds of thousands of Americans could die from the virus.
content:
Dr. Anthony Fauci said Sunday that he anticipates the coronavirus could kill between 100,000 and 200,000 Americans while infecting "millions."
